    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Let your images support preview, zoom, share, swipe view and download.</p>
<h2 id="how-to-use"> How to use</h2>
<h3 id="install"> Install</h3>
<CodeGroup>
<CodeGroupItem title="yarn">
<div><pre><code><span>yarn</span> <span>add</span> -D vuepress-plugin-photo-swipe
</code></pre>
<div><span>1</span><br></div></div></CodeGroupItem>
<CodeGroupItem title="npm">
<div><pre><code><span>npm</span> i -D vuepress-plugin-photo-swipe
</code></pre>
<div><span>1</span><br></div></div></CodeGroupItem>
</CodeGroup>
<h3 id="usage"> Usage</h3>
<div><pre><code><span>// .vuepress/config.js</span>
module<span>.</span>exports <span>=</span> <span>{</span>
  plugins<span>:</span> <span>[</span><span>"photo-swipe"</span><span>]</span><span>,</span>
<span>}</span><span>;</span>
</code></pre>
<div><span>1</span><br><span>2</span><br><span>3</span><br><span>4</span><br></div></div>]]></content>
